      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CELEBRITY CRUISE (1) did well to finish fourth two starts ago at Dubbo but came back to earth at her latest appearance over 1730m at Bathurst, beaten 35 metres into ninth after being close to the pace throughout. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. The recent run not a true indication. Good enough to put herself right in the finish. ALTIANO (7) has had three runs this prep without filling a placing. Was again unable to find the frame last start when he finished sixth over 1730m at Bathurst, beaten 6 metres. Won't spend a penny from this draw but luck may play a role on the bell lap. Tackles a similar assignment and he can make sharp improvement. IDEAL TAO (9) owns a good record at this circuit and distance and was solid from this row last start. ROCK QUEEN (4) is in the mix after turning in a better effort last start to finish second at Young.",
